==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: Not seeing (somebody) for a day is like being apart for three autumns.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: yī rì bù jiàn, rú gé sān qiū

===Idiom===
'''[[一]][[日]][[不]][[見]]，[[如]][[隔]][[三]][[秋]]'''

# A single day apart seems like three years.

===Alternate forms===
[[一日不见，如隔三秋]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

===Related terms===
[[一]][[日]][[三]][[秋]]

